<plot>Love hides a strange and deadly secret in this short thriller from filmmaker Brandon Harris. Adia is a college student attending the New School in New York City. Aida's family boasts a certain amount of celebrity that sometimes makes it difficult for her classmates to relate to her -- her mother is a famous media-savvy evangelist, and her father is a respected novelist. As Adia tries to overcome her academic challenges, she suspects that her boyfriend is hiding a secret from her. At first, Adia is convinced that her new man is bisexual, but in time she learns that his secret life is a very different (and very dangerous) kettle of fish.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?183852</url></doc>
